  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This one time pilot laboratory study focuses on examining the relationship between different
      types of physical tasks and taste perception of high and low-calorie foods among hungry
      individuals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
